OL,3,CSlip and slide attractions slashed in
OL,4,CCornwall
OL,6,FTwo slip and slide tourist attractions
OL,7,Fin Cornwall have been left thousands
OL,8,Fof pounds out of pocket after being
OL,9,Ftargeted by vandals.
OL,11,FThe first attack happened at Mega Slip
OL,12,Fand Slide, in Blackwater, near Truro,
OL,13,Fovernight on Thursday 15 August.
OL,15,FIt was followed by a second attack at
OL,16,FAvalanche Slip n Slide in East Crinnis
OL,17,FHoliday Park, near St Austell, on
OL,18,FMonday 26 August, in which four slides
OL,19,Fwere badly damaged.
