OL,6,FIt is believed the slides were slashed
OL,7,Fwith a sharp object.
OL,9,FDevon and Cornwall Police said it has
OL,10,Freceived reports of criminal damage at
OL,11,Fthe attractions and is appealing for
OL,12,Fanyone with information to come
OL,13,Fforward.
OL,15,FDominic McCalwane, owner of Mega Slip
OL,16,Fand Slide, said he was "very
OL,17,Fdisappointed" after discovering one of
OL,18,Fthe slides had been vandalised.
OL,20,F"Our customers, they come here for the
OL,21,Fsmiles and for a good time," he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
