OL,6,F"It's disappointing for myself as a
OL,7,Fbusiness owner, but also for the
OL,8,Fcommunity because we bring a lot of
OL,9,Fpeople through this little village."
OL,11,FMr McCalwane said he has spent around
OL,12,F#10,000 repairing the slip and slide
OL,13,Fand installing security cameras at the
OL,14,Fsite in order to be able to continue
OL,15,Ftrading.
OL,17,F"We've now got 4K imagery of the whole
OL,18,Fsite," he said. "We don't expect to
OL,19,Factually have to do that."
