OL,6,FHe added: "It's strange to see a CCTV
OL,7,Fcamera but you have to adapt and
OL,8,Fovercome."
OL,10,FDan Olford, owner of East Crinnis
OL,11,FHoliday Park, said he has been forced
OL,12,Fto close Avalanche Slip n Slide for
OL,13,Fthe foreseeable future due to the
OL,14,Fscale of the damage.
OL,16,F"We've been through the emotional
OL,17,Frollercoaster of feeling very hurt,
OL,18,Fsad, and upset, trying to understand
OL,19,Fwhy someone would do something like
OL,20,Fthis," he said.
