OL,6,FMr Olford said it will cost thousands
OL,7,Fof pounds to repair the slides, which
OL,8,Fare currently not fit for purpose.
OL,10,FDevon and Cornwall Police said it is
OL,11,Fno longer investigating reports of
OL,12,Fcriminal damage at Mega Slip and Slide
OL,13,Fin Truro.
OL,15,F"At this time, there are no viable
OL,16,Flines of enquiry however if further
OL,17,Fevidence comes to light the incident
OL,18,Fcan be re-visited," a police
OL,19,Fspokesperson said.
